field.value:
If we have view with ViewComponents - in my case AuthenticatedContent , then compiled brail assembly contains following code:

public override void Run()
{
    ....
    ViewComponent component = ((IViewComponentFactory)   RuntimeServices.DuckImplicitCast(MonoRailHttpHandler.CurrentContext.GetService(typeof(IViewComponentFactory)), typeof(IViewComponentFactory))).Create("AuthenticatedContent");
    ....
}

This  code requires HttpContext  and will not allow to render view in tests derived from BaseControllerTest - it will fail with NullReferenceException. Please modify this to get IViewComponentFactory from IRailsEngineContext instance passed to BrailBase.
